    "3": {
      "name": "Ahmed Zayed, MD",
      "role": "Physician & Medical Writer",
      "bio": "Ahmed Zayed, MD, is a physician, an author, and a fitness lover, and he has a deep-seated desire to assist others in leading happier and more fulfilling lives.\r\n\r\nDr. Ahmed Zayed, who received his degree in medicine and surgery from the University of Alexandria, is committed to sharing his expertise with his audience and believes that readers deserve accurate information.\r\n\r\nDr. Zayed has the ability to explain difficult ideas in a way that a layperson can understand while still incorporating a scientific perspective into the discussions that surround those ideas."
    },
    "4": {
      "name": "Theo de Vries",
      "role": "Founder",
      "bio": "“The first question is not why the addiction; it’s why the pain?”\r\nGabor Maté\r\n\r\nTheo de Vries, 45 years old, father of three children, married to Panwadee de Vries, has lived full-time in Thailand since 2012.\r\n\r\n“Not every client is the same, and everyone needs a different approach.”\r\n\r\nTheo’s favourite quote comes from Gabor Maté. “The first question is not why the addiction – it’s why the pain?”\r\n\r\nIf you decide to go to The Diamond rehab center in Thailand, you will be treated as such – respectful, personalized approach, and above all, as a human being. Theo is aware that the success of the client’s recovery starts with the person’s willingness and hard work to change; excellent therapy will do the rest."
    },
    "5": {
      "name": "Vladimira Ivanova",
      "role": "Psychologist",
      "bio": "Vladimira Ivanova is a dedicated psychologist with a passion for helping others.\r\n\r\nShe practices Systemic Individual, Family, and Marital Psychotherapy. In a social rehabilitation and integration center for elderly women and a psychological counseling and rehabilitation center, Vladimira has helped people discover and grow. Vladimira helped addicts and crisis families. She works with each person’s dynamics and environment. She wants to make important issues like addiction more accessible and raise awareness."
    },
    "12": {
      "name": "Asif Baliyan, MD",
      "role": "Consultant Histopathologist",
      "bio": "Dr. Baliyan, an Associate Consultant in Histopathology &amp; Cytopathology, brings expertise in Pathology, Oncopathology, AI Pathology, and quality management. With a track record in top Indian healthcare providers and freelance work in the USA.\r\n\r\nDriven by a commitment to quality, Dr. Baliyan looks forward to making a positive impact in healthcare collaborations."
    },
    "10": {
      "name": "Dr. Harshi Dhingra",
      "role": "Consultant Pathologist",
      "bio": ""
    }
  },
